      "updated": 1778033923868,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Jis user ke paas se\nrequest aa rahi hai\nusko identify karna.\n=> lets say, there are\n10,000 users hitting one\nserver -> which user at\nparticular instance of\nhitted the server\n(making a request)\n-> this we will identify by\nauthentication.\nby authentication them,\nwe get to know that\nthis particular user make\na request.",
      "fontSize": 13.191722602242512,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Jis user ke paas se\nrequest aa rahi hai\nusko identify karna.\n=> lets say, there are\n10,000 users hitting one\nserver -> which user at\nparticular instance of\nhitted the server\n(making a request)\n-> this we will identify by\nauthentication.\nby authentication them,\nwe get to know that\nthis particular user make\na request.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "9tHkXMJ_Hs1pa4OFQIM81",
